      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_075_000057",
    "sentence": "勝同產弟子賞為梁內史，梁內史子定國為豫章太守。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 20,
        "end": 22
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_075_000058",
    "sentence": "而建子千秋亦為少府、太子少傅。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 12
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_075_000059",
